></div><div data-aura-rendered-by="18:265;a" role="listitem" data-aura-class="forcePageBlockSectionRow"><p><span data-aura-rendered-by="31:265;a"><table data-aura-rendered-by="32:265;a"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" rowspan="1">
<h2>Cloud Services Application Essentials</h2>
</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1">
<div><p>Welcome to the Ivanti® EPM Cloud Services Application (CSA) landing page.&nbsp;From here you can access product downloads and documentation or link to useful configuration and troubleshooting guides. Using the icons above you can search the knowledge base, participate in forums and engage with Support.</p><p>Our <a href="https://help.ivanti.com/docs/help/en_US/LDMS/11.0/Windows/welcome.htm">online help documentation</a>&nbsp;is readily available to assist you in addition to our Community resources linked below.</p><p>The current product release for the CSA is the CSA 5.0.7 available for download here: <a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/CSA-5-0-Download?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">Ivanti Cloud Services Application 5.0 Download, Release Notes, &amp; Patch History</a></p></div>
</td></tr></tbody></table>

<table data-aura-rendered-by="32:265;a"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" rowspan="1">
<h2>Latest CSA Updates</h2>
</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td colspan="1" rowspan="1">

<p>Stay informed and up-to-date with the latest enhancement and improvements to EPM. Hit the subscribe button above!<br>&nbsp;</p>
<ul><li>March 10, 2026: CSA 5.0.7 was released.</li><li>September 3, 2025: CSA 5.0.6 was released.&nbsp;</li><li>May 13, 2025: CSA 5.0.5 Security Mitigation Update. <a href="https://forums.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-Cloud-Services-Application-CVE-2025-22460?language=en_US" title="Security Advisory Ivanti Cloud Services Application (CVE-2025-22460)">Security Advisory Ivanti Cloud Services Application (CVE-2025-22460)</a></li><li>February 11, 2025: CSA 5.0.5 was released.&nbsp;<a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-Cloud-Services-Application-CSA-CVE-2024-47908-CVE-2024-11771?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">Security Advisory Ivanti Cloud Services Application (CSA) (CVE-2024-47908, CVE-2024-11771)</a></li><li>January 6, 2025: CSA 5.0.4 was released.&nbsp;</li><li>December 10, 2024: CSA 5.0.3 was released. Please see&nbsp;<a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-Cloud-Services-Application-CSA-CVE-2024-11639-CVE-2024-11772-CVE-2024-11773?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">Security Advisory Ivanti Cloud Services Application (CSA) (CVE-2024-11639, CVE-2024-11772, CVE-2024-11773)</a></li><li>October 16, 2024: There is a Hot Patch for the CSA 5.0:&nbsp;<a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/CSA-5-0-2-Hot-Patch?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">CSA 5.0.2 Hot Patch</a></li><li>October 8, 2024: CSA 5.0.2 was released. There is a security advisory for the CSA 4.6. If you have not yet updated to the new CSA 5.0, please see&nbsp;<a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-CSA-Cloud-Services-Appliance-CVE-2024-9379-CVE-2024-9380-CVE-2024-9381?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">Security Advisory Ivanti CSA (Cloud Services Appliance) (CVE-2024-9379, CVE-2024-9380, CVE-2024-9381)</a></li><li>September 10, 2024: There is a security advisory for the CSA 4.6. If you have not yet updated to the CSA 5.0, please see&nbsp;<a href="https://hub.ivanti.com/s/article/Security-Advisory-Ivanti-Cloud-Service-Appliance-CSA-CVE-2024-8190?ui-force-components-controllers-recordGlobalValueProvider.RecordGvp.getRecord=1">Security Advisory Ivanti Cloud Service Appliance (CSA) (CVE-2024-8190)</a></li><li>Important changes are coming to the CSA in 2024: <a href="https://forums.ivanti.com/s/article/Ivanti-CSA-Changing-from-Appliance-to-Application">Ivanti Cloud Services Appliance changing to Application</a></li></ul>

</td></tr></tbody></table>

<table data-aura-rendered-by="32:265;a"><thead><tr><th colspan="1" rowspan="1">
